                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1687" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0228</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8317 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雏鹰农牧股份有限公司股票期权行权条件的设计及其实施效果</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Vesting Conditions` Design and the Implementation Effect of Chuying Agro-pastoral Group Co., Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">袁振兴，王巧义等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北经贸大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雏鹰农牧股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股票期权；行权条件；期权激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">stock options; vesting conditions; stock options incentive</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了雏鹰农牧股份有限公司股票期权激励计划的行权条件及其实施效果。2012年3月13日雏鹰农牧股份有限公司发布《雏鹰农牧集团股份有限公司股票期权激励计划（草案修订稿）》，拟向公司董事、核心管理人员、中层管理人员、一般管理人员以及业务、技术岗位的骨干员工共计311名激励对象授予234万份公司股票期权。行权条件为：以2011年归属于上市公司股东扣除非经常性损益后的净利润为基数，2012年度归属于上市公司股东净利润增长率不低于10.00%（含）且扣除非经常性损益后加权平均净资产收益率不低15.00%。因没有达到《股权激励计划》的规定行权条件，2013年8月28日注销了已获授的第一个行权期对应的258.82万份股票期权（占已获授股票期权数量的40%）。雏鹰农牧股份有限公司的股票期权激励计划无果而终。本案例要讨论的问题是为什么股票期权激励计划无果而终？具体包括：实施股票期权激励的原因、股票期权激励的源条件、在股票期权契约设计和执行过程中的代理问题是如何产生的，公司代理问题以及其他因素是如何影响契约双方的行为，并最终影响股票期权激励效果的。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Chuying Agro-pastoral Group Co., Ltd. has implemented the “Chuying Agro-pastoral Group Co., Ltd. Stock Option Incentive Plan (revised draft)” in March 13, 2012. In this plan, the corporation intended to grant 2.35 million stock options to 313 incentive recipients including company directors, core management personnel, middle management, general management, and the backbone of the staff in business and technical positions. The vesting conditions is that compared to the shareholders of listed company&#39;s net profit after deducting non-recurring gains and losses, the net profit growth rate of shareholders of listed companies is no less than 10.00% or the weighted average return on net assets after deducting non-recurring gains and losses is no less than 15.00%.
Because of not reaching the vesting conditions of the “Stock Option Incentive Plan”，the incentive recipients’2.5882 million stock options (in the first exercise period) which was 40% of all the granted stock options was written off by directorate in August 28, 2013. The stock option incentive plan of Chuying Agro-pastoral Group Co., Ltd. had come to nothing. The case will discuss the reason to lead stock option incentive plan’s failure, including the reason to implement stock option incentive plan, initial condition of the stock option incentive, the agent problem during the procedure of designing and carrying out the stock option incentive, how the agent problem and related factors affect the behaviors of two sides of contract and the result of stock option incentive. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理学》、《高级财务管理》、《公司投融资理论与方法》、《财务会计理论》、《金融市场与金融工具》、《投资学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股票期权激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
